Globe is a tool for monitoring applications through the Como sources.

BEFORE COMPILATION

 * Copy QtConfFile directory into the root from https://github.com/igormironchik/qt-conf-file
 * Copy QtArg directory into the the root from https://github.com/igormironchik/qtargparser
 * Copy Como directory into the root from https://github.com/igormironchik/components-observation
 
COMPILLING
 * Run qmake and make
 